        style=&quot;background-color: white; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 0.00266667px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;is to manipulate files that consist of fields separated by delimiters, such as a comma separated values (CSV) or configuration file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 0.00266667px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span
